rong><span>🏀 </span><a href=\"https://figureitoutsportsbetting.substack.com/p/knicks-consistently-a-little-bit?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=1895386&amp;post_id=202056511&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><span>Knicks Consistently A Little Bit Better than the Spurs: Stats Confirm What Most Observers Already Understood</span></a></strong><span>by </span> and <strong><a href=\"https://brianhoward.substack.com/p/dumb-money-smart-money-and-the-new\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Dumb Money, Smart Money, and the Knicks</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p>⚽ <strong><a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/athletic/7374458/2026/06/19/lionel-messi-referees-decisions/?source=dailyemail&amp;campaign=601983&amp;userId=295087&amp;source=dailyemail\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Do legends like Lionel Messi get treated differently by referees? Yes, but it’s complicated</a></strong> by Graham Scott</p></li>\n<li><p><strong><span>⚾ </span><a href=\"https://links.mlb.mlbemail.com/s/vb/B8ZpRWZJSUqxATknVAS4BVYexEN1GVZB42sW5-3m55AqXnFaRSJt5uzMJyvjgDmBa7t0zYeszaIi1gRztpsw3wB_22VaEhwyQ412PjBeGGp4dmTs6VOt8F698uvQ4PyttUASJY3QO0bKVg0gz5Y0JMa8RolxzhVy2Z-2Hw/2WNUTFNOT_0fXEw8lvPgv7VXYggqLUrq/21\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><span>So, the Cardinals are contenders. Now what?</span></a></strong><span> by </span> </p></li>\n<li><p><strong><span>⚾ </span><a href=\"https://baseballmath.substack.com/p/the-end-comes-sooner-than-later?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=1239485&amp;post_id=202374647&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><span>The End Comes Sooner Than Later</span></a></strong><span> by </span> </p></li>\n<li><p><span>⚾ </span><strong><a href=\"https://baseballscoops.substack.com/p/5-players-that-should-be-traded-at?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=3048797&amp;post_id=202226396&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><span>5 Players that Should be Traded at the MLB Deadline</span></a></strong><span> by </span> </p></li>\n<li><p><strong><span>⚾ </span><a href=\"https://ibwaa.substack.com/p/when-60-war-doesnt-feel-like-cooperstown?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=96452&amp;post_id=202316897&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><span>When 60+ WAR Doesn't Feel Like Cooperstown</span></a></strong><span> by </span> </p></li>\n<li><p><span>⚾ </span><strong><a href=\"https://baseballspast.substack.com/p/the-other-dimaggio-streak?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=6364294&amp;post_id=201458155&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><span>The Other DiMaggio Streak</span></a></strong><span> by </span> </p></li>\n<li><p><span>⚾ </span><strong><a href=\"https://jasher.substack.com/p/laz-diaz-is-an-above-average-home?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=1234332&amp;post_id=200154702&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><span>Laz Diaz is an Above-Average Home Plate Umpire All of a Sudden</span></a></strong><span> by </span> </p></li>\n<li><p><span>⚾ </span><strong><a href=\"https://almostametnewsletter.substack.com/p/michael-bourn-mets-rumors-mike-mayer?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=1352443&amp;post_id=187900742&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" t